## 🧱 Technical Fixes
- Ensure all pages have unique and optimized title tags and meta descriptions
- Improve internal linking structure to distribute page authority and improve crawlability
- Optimize images with descriptive alt text and compress them to improve page load speed

## 💡 Conversion Optimization
- Add clear and compelling calls-to-action on product and category pages
- Implement trust signals such as customer reviews, ratings, and secure payment badges
- Simplify the checkout process to reduce cart abandonment and improve conversions

